<title>USA: Continental Homes Holding Corp Q4 net rises.</title>
<headline>Continental Homes Holding Corp Q4 net rises.</headline>
<dateline>SCOTTSDALE, Ariz. 1997-06-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>Quarter Ended May 31</p>
<p>				1997			1996</p>
<p> Shr primary		$0.82		    $0.43</p>
<p> Shr diluted		$0.62		    $0.36</p>
<p> Net			  5,659		    3,029</p>
<p> Revs		     165,305		  171,583</p>
<p>		  YEAR</p>
<p> Shr primary		$4.24		    $2.71</p>
<p> Shr diluted		$3.10		    $2.27</p>
<p> Net			 29,445		   18,869</p>
<p> Revs		     681,838		  577,073</p>
<p>(All data above 000s except per share numbers)</p>
<p>NOTE: Net income for the quarter and fiscal year ended May 31, 1996, included a net extraordinary loss of $6.9 million and $6.06 million, respectively, due to the write-off of unamortized discount and debt issuance costs related to the redemption of convertible suborinated notes, and the write-off of debt issuance costs related to the repurchase of a majority of the company's 12 percent senior notes due August 1999.</p>
</text>
